{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to the simulator of the New Year 2025 Demo! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">New Year is a bright, kind, holiday filled with joy, fun and magic. I think many of us have a lot of warm memories and emotions associated with this holiday. This holiday is always eagerly awaited by both adults and children. But still, it's hard to argue with the fact that it is in childhood that this holiday feels special. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is the main task of this simulator - to provide an opportunity for the player to immerse himself in that unforgettable atmosphere from childhood, which reigns on New Year's Eve. We will dive into it on behalf of the main character - a 12-year-old boy Anton. A calm voiceover will help with the narration. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278640/extras/Window1.gif?t=1732716308\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The demo takes 20-25 minutes to complete.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features of the game: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- First-person view. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Dynamic storytelling. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Realistic interaction system. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Complete freedom of movement around the location. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Realistic soundtrack.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Dynamic change of the time of day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278640/extras/ELKA2.gif?t=1732716308\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in the holiday atmosphere with your head!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278640/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732716308","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278640